{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "RestMan - Auth Service API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for RestMan Authentication Service\n\n**Features:**\n- OTP-based email authentication\n- Session management (2-hour validity)\n- Support for 3 user roles: user, rest, kitch\n- Redis-backed sessions\n- CockroachDB user storage\n- Kafka event publishing\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:8001\n\n**Workflow:**\n1. Request OTP → Email sent with 6-digit code (5-min expiry)\n2. Verify OTP → Returns session token\n3. Use session token for authenticated requests\n4. Logout → Invalidates session",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "restman-auth"
	},
